{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-20", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "臨近的暴風", "storyInfo": "羅德島得到Outcast犧牲的消息，正式準備向倫蒂尼姆進發。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......都給我吧。為了把她送回來，你趕了一路，很辛苦。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下面的事，我親自處理。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺物和骨灰匣。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切爾諾伯格事件結束後，類似的緊急通訊聲已經有整整十一個月又二十七天沒有在羅德島的甲板上響起了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這一次犧牲的是誰？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Outcast。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了，你手中握著的是她的彈巢。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然不想承認，但在來的路上，我已經想過這個答案。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經和她打過一個賭——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，她還是贏了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希，下面的會議，我會缺席。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照慣例，精英幹員的葬禮將由你親自主持......", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這次，我希望由我來告別她。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想沒有人會有異議，包括她自己。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然會議中止，那麼，我會在這裡給出我最終的選擇——", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Misery，我知道你的答案。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你肯定也知道其他人的答案。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況發生了變化。沒人喜歡這個變化，但大家都清楚只能這麼選。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我們必須儘快進入倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都很清楚，我的立場始終如一——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但無論你們最終是否決定支持我的提議，我都必須強調，羅德島並不會為了宣洩任何私人情感而決定未來的航向。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_235"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在提醒我，不要想著為Outcast報仇？", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你放心。我的內心是充滿了悲痛和憤怒，可我還記得自己的職責。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我要親眼看一看能殺死Outcast的究竟是什麼——", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不會是一個人，或者幾個人。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希......假如我們不去尋找真相，那麼籠罩著倫蒂尼姆乃至整個維多利亞的陰雲只會更加肆無忌憚。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，不止Outcast......", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會死，我們都會。沒有人能逃脫。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你說的，羅德島不會為了死者復仇......", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我們都想為生者創造繼續活下去的機會。", "name": "Misery"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_235"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_canteen"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......這是什麼地方？我是不是又走錯路了？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟糕，快到約好的時間了，我得快點走......唉，奧利弗叔叔怎麼沒說過，這艘船有這麼大呀！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，你是......？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，請、請等一下！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（為什麼她看起來就像完全不認識我？）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不，我不可能認錯人。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（上船之後，好幾次想找人問問她怎麼樣了，但他們都要嘛不知道，要嘛不告訴我。）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唔......為了她的安全，也許這是更妥當的做法？）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你好。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你是在這裡看書嗎？這本《騎士艾凡赫傳奇》......我也看過，而且很喜歡。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "書裡描寫的那段維多利亞歷史很有趣，不是嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有趣......嗎？還好......但不是真的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小說......就只是小說而已。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......這麼說也沒錯。你還想看其他小說嗎？我有好多......呃，對不起，我忘了自己都沒帶出來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你喜歡這本......可以送給你。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，這樣好嗎？謝、謝謝......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我走了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊好的，再見！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......還能再見嗎？）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（她手裡的另一本書是......詩集？）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西莫·威廉姆斯......作者姓名和封面都好眼熟。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約好的地方......就是這裡了？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "識、識別碼？那是什麼東西？《新幹員指引》裡有寫嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，馬上就要遲到了，還是先敲下門試試吧！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進來吧！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I14", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下午好，薇洛小姐......還是應該叫你幹員琴柳？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......阿米婭小姐！", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請和大家一樣叫我阿米婭吧。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是不好意思......阿米婭這麼忙，還要抽時間來見我。前兩天體檢的時候，亞葉小姐說你一天只休息五個小時......", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞葉姐姐總是很擔心我的身體。不過沒關係，我最近的健康狀況很不錯，而且我也一直很想再見見你。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這裡就是Outcast以前的辦公室？", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。其實她並沒有在這裡待很久，出事前兩個月，我們剛剛說服她接受了崗位調動。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她和我說過，在來小丘郡之前，她已經差不多半退休了......", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她依然堅持申請去執行這次任務。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我時常回想她在那幾天說的每一句話......我相信她早就做好了面對一切的準備。", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Outcast確實是這樣的人。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便是在精英幹員中，Outcast的性格都稱得上特別——她總能輕鬆地做出一些普通人眼裡很艱難的決定。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，她說......她曾經因為一次戰爭中的失敗調停，放棄了教會裡很高的職位。", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......離開拉特蘭教會的部分確有其事，但是失敗的調停？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得Outcast的檔案裡有這項記載，反而，這聽起來很像Misery的一件往事。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈......不知道為什麼，這很像她會做的事。", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能有些人會因此覺得Outcast不夠真誠......", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，即便你告訴我，她說的並不全是實話，她仍是我見過最真誠的人。", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的這麼想？嗯......我並不是很意外，畢竟Outcast看人的眼光從不出錯。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，我理解你的時間很寶貴......但你願不願意再多跟我說一些她的故事？", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，這故事會很長——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你有空，我隨時想聽。", "name": "琴柳"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啊，我相信......去倫蒂尼姆的路上，我們會有很多時間的。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數月後"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_safehouseindoor"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底修好了沒啊？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別著急嘛，這鎮子太荒了，要找到個能給發報機用的替換線圈很不容易......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是我來吧。你這輕輕一碰設備就冒煙的問題，看來根本沒好轉。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來這安全屋也很久沒人用了嘛......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到底，我就不該聽你的走這條路線。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾個月兜兜轉轉，一半時間都在沒人煙的地方吃沙！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾年沒見，陳陳你怎麼瞪起人來更凶了......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別嘟囔了，根本不夠小聲，我都聽得見。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#2"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問我為什麼著急？我還納悶你怎麼不急！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一趟出來多久了，別說鬼魂部隊，我們連個像樣的線索都沒找到！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換作我還在龍門當警察的時候，遇到這種情況，我都想叫你趕緊死心......沒什麼人質能撐這麼久。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道隊長一定還活著。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同樣的，她知道我會想辦法救她，她也會想盡辦法來和我會合。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#6"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。算了算了，我真是拿你沒辦法。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#6"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能說服你，我至於被你拽著到處跑這麼久？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#6"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那當然是因為......陳陳你一直都對我這麼好！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#6"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，你的執著，我不是不明白。那些年，我滿心想著找那個人的時候，你也始終支持著我......算了，眼下不提這個。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#6"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——總之，你也都聽到了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小丘郡事件對外宣稱早有定論，就是一場軍隊演習事故。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有受傷和生病的平民都得到了賠償和安置——至少政府文件裡就是這麼寫的。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池，或者說鬼魂部隊，無論在你離開時候他們是不是佔領了小丘郡，現在看起來都已經悄無聲息地撤離了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一點，就算我們回去親眼確認，也不會改變。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同意。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還記得我看見的全部。我相信，再怎麼貌似平靜，小丘郡內部......以及周圍很多城市裡，都還是發生了很大的變化。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......一想到這些變化在眾目睽睽之下被藏得這麼好，陳陳你不覺得更恐怖了嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果敵人在鬧出了這麼大動靜之後選擇了再次蟄伏，那只能說明，他們背後還有更大的圖謀！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在維多利亞......隨時都會有比小丘郡更大的危機被引爆。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我信你。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以我在這裡。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我沒有把握還有多少人會信你。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是為什麼我們要繼續努力！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼看，我們還是得想辦法進入大城市。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得休斯吧？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個......胖胖的訓練時候總是摔得滿頭包的男同學？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#5"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......人家已經是千貿城商業聯盟的副主席。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#5"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的話，是我們這幫同學裡，最有可能獲知一些被刻意藏起來的資訊的人。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#5"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，在陳陳你說之前，我早就想過去找休斯......不，不光休斯，我還想試試看找大個子格林，紅頭髮比爾......找大家幫忙！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些事，我一個人也試過，可是很難辦到......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是現在，我身邊有你，還有一路上羅德島的大家慷慨提供的物資和資訊支援——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感覺充滿了希望！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#2"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是得先提醒你，我沒把握他們能否被說服——啊？！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#2"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你*維多利亞問候語*幹什麼啊突然這麼大力拉我！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳陳，發報機亮了欸！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#3"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是羅德島的緊急電訊？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#3"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發報機壞了之前，他們才剛收到我們發出去的定位消息吧？難道說羅德島一直在找我......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#4"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ".........", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#4"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼啦？你的臉色就像剛才收到的資訊給你來了一整套拳......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我好像看懂了......又是關於她的消息？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你猜得沒錯。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#4"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#4"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#4"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來的事，我需要好好想一想。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#4"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_aircraft_2"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_156_1#1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，任務進行得怎麼樣？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我在路上了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能放鬆警惕。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，雷蛇前輩......雖然我沒怎麼回過維多利亞，但是我們的飛行器已經獲得了出入許可，導航系統也在正常運作中。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次護送僑民回哥倫比亞的任務說難不難，但隨時可能生變。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僑民給我們發信的時候，我還是有點驚訝的......", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一路上都還算風平浪靜，情況真、真的已經那麼嚴重了嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......抱歉，在隊長和隊員們面前不太好表現出來，可我確實還是有點緊張。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你的隊長不在？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是的，在到維多利亞之後不久，她就帶著一部分人走了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有可能......是有別的任務？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......撤僑行動被委託給了你們裝備與應用技術部門，這顯然是有原因的。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顯、顯然嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒發現，未嘗不是好事。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說......他們還在和別人談合作？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們並未收到任何維多利亞官方的訂單......", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......按照保密協定，我不該對跨部門的資訊進行猜測或評論。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請把我的這些話忘掉吧。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "專注你的任務，有什麼情況，隨時和我聯絡。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住，這次雖然是黑鋼接的任務，但我們和羅德島的合作依然有效。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_237", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我明白。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等羅德島的幾支小隊也順利靠近倫蒂尼姆，在必要的時候我會和他們互相接應。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_237"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bridge"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......越來越近了啊。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "維娜，你很緊張？;......;這一天我們都等了很久。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line330", "option2": "line336", "option3": "line340"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line343"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾個月前，凱爾希醫生問我是否準備好了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我的回答是，我不知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而到了這時候......我依舊不知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我很難說自己不緊張。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line343"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，謝謝你在這裡陪我。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我還在貪圖你身邊的這份清靜......我是不是顯得太逃避了？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line343"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，從我逃出來的那一天起，我就在等著回去的這一天。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我忍不住想，如果一個人離開他原本所屬的環境太久，他真的還有家可回嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "醒來的時候，我都不記得自己離開了多久。;阿米婭和大家都接納了我。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line348", "option2": "line352"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line355"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽你說起過那段日子。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你剛醒沒多久，就不得不站在指揮的位置上，經歷了切爾諾伯格那麼嚴重的事件......幾乎沒人能夠做到像你一樣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line355"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭......博士，你對阿米婭來說，是真正的家人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島需要你，我們這些幹員也都需要你，這一點毋庸置疑。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "在倫蒂尼姆，也有人等著你。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line360"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格拉斯哥幫。他們一定有了新的頭領，否則，他們無法在倫蒂尼姆立足。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於其他人......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信我離開這麼久，倫蒂尼姆壓根就不會少掉一枚釘子。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "想知道答案的話，就只能一起往前了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line368"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_112_seige_1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你說過......你也想去倫蒂尼姆尋找真相。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一起往前嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，確定有你們同行，我也能打起精神了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望，前方等待著我們的答案都不至於太糟糕......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，無論如何，我會努力用錘子把它錘出個過得去的模樣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "char_112_seige_1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hall_2"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是否都到了？", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快了，殿下，食腐者之王與血魔大君將在三日內抵達倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從王庭重新聚首，我們薩卡茲正處於內戰後最接近統一的階段。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能讓任何勢力擋在我們面前。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起其他勢力，殿下，那名來自小丘郡的使者至今仍在倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事已有結論。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如殿下先前說的那樣，他們並非真心想要結盟。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個有誠意的盟友，不會把自己藏在幕後，連半張臉都不露，只把一個半瘋半傻的僕人丟到我們面前。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不可能得到想要的，卻並沒有就此離去。她帶來的部隊，在倫蒂尼姆外圍與貴族殘黨和當地居民發生了多次衝突。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "試探。他們想刺探倫蒂尼姆的現狀，同時評估我們的實力。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，殿下，如果我們表現得軟弱，她背後的人將會提前入局。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而如果我們態度強硬，她就是一枚失去價值的棄子，被剪除了也並不可惜。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想讓薩卡茲當刀子的陰謀家，最後都會死於刀下。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她甚至不及塔露拉。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然有著相近的血脈，但深池的領袖與塔露拉截然不同。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與整合運動相比，深池在南部掀起的波瀾，足以證明他們有足夠的武力，做好了或者正在做著撕扯維多利亞的準備。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一群趁亂獲利的人，只有在混亂到達頂點時，才會現身。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現階段，只要和我們眼前的目標和薩卡茲無關，無論他們在外面有何謀劃，都不值得我關心。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是在倫蒂尼姆，我不允許節外生枝。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓曼弗雷德順帶把這事處理了。應付那些貴族對他來說太簡單，他需要儘快成長。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德向來知道你的想法，他已經做好了準備。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不夠。羅德島有什麼新動向？", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾個月，他們沒有停止過正常的、表面上的“商業活動”。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那艘陸上艦船在去年年底駛離卡西米爾以後，曾多次靠近維多利亞，但並沒有長時間脫離過我們的視線。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要他們靠近倫蒂尼姆......不，只要那幾個人進入維多利亞， 立刻向我彙報。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，你可以直接向她報告。", "name": "攝政王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_055"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，殿下——薩卡茲的王，自然知道該如何去回收屬於她的冠冕。", "name": "赦罪師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_055"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ep09", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}